race.description: Magic Millions Yearling Sales Mar 12-13 Mdn Plate
race.comment: SMOKIN REELS (2) didn't have much luck as favourite and then rode the speed here over 1300m beaten 1.6L. Presents fitter again and will jump and run from the inside barrier. That may provide the edge required. NEXT STOP JUPITER (13) debuted over 1200m on the same day, beaten less than 1L. Had to work pushing forward and draws even wider today. Fitter now and will go close with average luck in the run. VOUCHERS (10) is a former Victorian who resumed here 10 days ago in solid order. He's right up to this at best, but also has an awkward gate to contend with. Wiggins stays aboard and that's a positive. NOTFORTHEMONEY (8) has the cruellest draw, but he's an improver in good hands and should be around the mark.
